dc_creator_sm: Smithsonian Institution, Global Volcanism Program, National Atlas of the United States, and the United States Geological Survey
National Atlas of the United States, and the U.S. Geological Survey
dc_description_s: U.S. National Atlas Volcanoes represents volcanoes thought to be active in the last 10,000 years (Holocene), in and near the United States. The data is a subset of data available from the Global Volcanism Program, Smithsonian Institution.
